snippet.title: Orcs Must Die! - Unchained Announcement Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Orcs Must Die! Unchained
is a fast-paced Fortress Siege action game in which teams of heroes battle head-to-head to attack and defend ancient strongholds. 

http://www.orcsmustdie.com
http://www.facebook.com/OMDGame
http://www.twitter.com/OrcsMustDie

For the first time in Orcs Must Die!, teams of players are responsible for both sides of the battle -- building traps to stop the enemy assault AND summoning their own armies to lead against the enemy defense.
 
http://www.orcsmustdie.com

May contain content inappropriate for children, visit www.esrb.org for rating information
